                        <p class="card-text">The visit was to interact with the Governor with a view to promoting the understanding of DPR’s regulatory role in the oil and gas.</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-success mt-1" href="https://www.dpr.gov.ng/news-updates/" target="_blank">Read More..</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="card" style="width: 20rem;">
                    <img src="~/app-assets/images/DPR-MPR_building_complex.png" class="card-img-top" />
                    <img  />


                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h6>NIGERIA’S PROVEN GAS RESERVE NOW 203.16TCF, SAYS DPR</h6>
                        <p class="card-text">In line with our stakeholders engagement strategy, the Zonal Operations controller, DPR Maiduguri Mr. Ibrahim Ciroma paid a courtesy.</p>
                        <a class="btn btn-success mt-1" href="https://www.dpr.gov.ng/news-updates/" target="_blank">Read More..</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="section bg-light-gray" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-3">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 offset-2">
                <form>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label>Name</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label>Email</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" />
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-12">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label>Message</label>
                                <textarea class="form-control"></textarea>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Contact us</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


